{"about_the_game":"<strong>Cozy Dungeons</strong> is an adventure/interior design game where you explore dungeons, clear them out of enemies and renovate them for a profit! Take control of the leader of a monster extermination guild that decides to add a decorative spin to the business. After all, why just conquer a dungeon when you can turn it into a B&amp;B?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EXPLORE TREACHEROUS DUNGEONS</h2>Make your way through dungeons full of devious puzzles, vicious enemies and lethal traps. Use a variety of tools that will help you in exploration and combat, and keep your wits about you - they might just give you the edge you need to survive.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377600/extras/explore.gif?t=1736370420\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">UNLEASH YOUR INNER RENOVATOR</h2>Every dungeon you visit belongs to a client, and they want to see it looking brand-new! Build new furniture, clean up garbage, change the walls and floor, sell broken furniture and much more! Once you\u2019re all set, let the gold roll in!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377600/extras/renovate.gif?t=1736370420\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CUSTOMIZE YOUR GUILD</h2>You can spend your hard-earned gold to decorate and expand your Guild however you want, improve your character, buy new blueprints, meet new friends and more - the sky\u2019s the limit!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377600/extras/guild.gif?t=1736370420\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377600/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736370420","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377600/page.bg.jpg?t=1736370420","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377600/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736370420","